 We don't see that as we get older and, you know, grow up in Hong Kong, this busy place

113
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:44,760
 full of pressure.

114
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,760
 Right?

115
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:49,920
 And why is it that she's able to be so free and joyful?

116
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:55,800
 And okay, now, first of all, disclaimer, I don't have a PhD in child development or anything

117
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,800
 like that.

118
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,800
 All right?

119
